    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The implementation of disaster planning, incident preparedness, a disaster recovery plan; and a subset of business continuity. In conservation context, interventions on behalf of structures and artifacts affected by man made or natural disaster.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
